The evidence with the title 'Monsanto Co. v. Geertson Seed Farms - Wikipedia ' says Monsanto Co. vs. Geertson Seed Farms, 561 U.S. 139 (2010), is a United States Supreme Court case decided 7 - 1 in favor of Monsanto.The decision allowed Monsanto to sell genetically modified alfalfa seeds to farmers , and allowed farmers to plant them , grow crops, harvest them, and sell the crop into the food supply . 
